com.esri.mo2.map.draw
Interface GroupRenderer

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable, LegendInfo, Renderer
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseGroupRenderer
public interface GroupRenderer
extends Renderer

Draws a FeatureClass using a list of renderers. The renderes are drawn in the order that they are added. The following is an example of how GroupRenderers can be accessed:


     com.esri.mo2.map.draw.Renderer renderer = aFeatureLayer.getRenderer();
     com.esri.mo2.map.draw.GroupRenderer gr = (com.esri.mo2.map.draw.GroupRenderer)renderer;
     try {
            gr.removeRendererAt(0);
            int pos = gr.addRenderer(aRend);
            gr.moveRenderer(2, 0);
      } catch ( Exception e ) {
            com.esri.mo2.util.MessageCentre.get().log(this,e);
      }
